title: BRIEF-MSC Konsult AB changes name to MSC Group AB as of Sept 8
text:
BRIEF-MSC Konsult AB changes name to MSC Group AB as of Sept 8 Sept 3 
Sept 3 MSC Konsult AB : 
* As from Sept. 8, MSC Konsult AB will be listed under its new company name, MSC Group AB
